data.description: Honey stop the car!!! This impeccable rehabbed 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths Brick Raised Ranch, 2 Car Garage is surely your Dream Home. This open concept floor plan boast of Gleaming Harwood floors throughout. Enjoy cooking your favorite meals in your All White Kitchen with 42 inch Cabinetry, Beautiful Pristine Stone Countertops with a stunning backsplash and Stainless Steel Appliances. This beauty also features White raised Panel Doors,   all New Windows, 3 main level Generous size Bedrooms with a Full Finished Basement featuring an additional Bedroom & 1 Full Bath for Guest or to accommodate a growing family. This Home has plenty of Storage & a Huge Laundry Room, Washer & Dryer included. Make your Oasis in this Huge Back yYard for the Best Retreats for bar-b-ques & summertime fun.  DONT MISS OUT TOUR TODAY BEFORE ITS GONE!
